クラスの使用
com.ntt.tc.data.sensor.Value

  • Valueを使用しているパッケージ 
    パッケージ 説明
    com.ntt.tc.data  
    com.ntt.tc.data.sensor  

    • com.ntt.tc.dataでのValueの使用

      Valueとして宣言されているcom.ntt.tc.dataのフィールド 
      修飾子とタイプ フィールドと説明
      Value C8y_Battery.level
      c8y_Battery shows the current battery fill level.
      Value C8y_Mobile.rssi
      RSSI measurement "unit":dBm

    • com.ntt.tc.data.sensorでのValueの使用

      Valueとして宣言されているcom.ntt.tc.data.sensorのフィールド 
      修飾子とタイプ フィールドと説明
      Value C8y_AccelerationMeasurement.acceleration
      Measured acceleration along the sensor axis (direction of the sensor axis is not defined in this measurement).
      Value C8y_SignalStrength.ber 
      Value C8y_CurrentMeasurement.current
      Current measurement "unit":"A"
      Value C8y_DistanceMeasurement.distance
      Distance measurement "unit":"mm"
      Value C8y_LightMeasurement.e
      Photometrical Light Measurement "unit":"lux"
      Value C8y_HumidityMeasurement.h
      Relative Humidity measurement "unit":"%RH"
      Value C8y_MoistureMeasurement.moisture
      Relative Moisture measurement "unit":"%"
      Value C8y_MotionMeasurement.motionDetected
      Boolean value indicating if motion has been detected (non-zero value) or not (zero value).
      Value C8y_SignalStrength.rssi 
      Value C8y_MotionMeasurement.speed
      Measured speed towards (+ve) or away (-ve) from the sensor.
      Value C8y_TemperatureMeasurement.T
      Measured temperature.
      Value C8y_VoltageMeasurement.voltage
      Voltage measurement "unit":"V"
